data.description: Luxury floorplan that cannot be matched! Access to the private quarters thru double solid doors from the main foyer and the social areas to the right. High ceilings, formal living and dining with large wet bar perfect for entertaining! Walk-in coat closet. Spacious office or game room with built-ins, half bath with access from foyer. A second private area features a hallway to the spacious laundry and huge mud-room built-ins for more storage! A 5th room for guests or maids with its own closet and full bath! Kitchen has island and counter with its own dining area that can seat 8-10, a large dream pantry and amazing living room with views to the pool. Private rooms include 2 masters with private baths and walk-in closets and 2 large rooms with shared full bath. Master has a dream closet with island and plenty of drawers. Outdoor large covered patio, gas fireplace with seating area, pergola, pool with retractable cover, wet bar, full bath and large pool room! Community ponds available!
